    "This is because the primary goal of software testing is to identify issues or problems in the software system, rather than to generate correct code or meet specific software requirements.",
    "At worst, the only consequence is that the corresponding defects are not discovered.",
    "Furthermore, in some cases, the seemingly incorrect outputs from LLMs may be beneficial for testing corner cases in software and can help uncover defects.",
    "Taken in this sense, we think the LLMs are a natural match with software testing\".",
    "«Системні технології» 2 (151) 2024 «System technologies» ISSN 1562-9945 (Print) ISSN 2707-7977 (Online) 120 Thus, the question arises whether, at this stage of generative AI development, it is possible to achieve automatic generation of a sufficiently complete set of tests and whether it should be pursued."
